Raquel Rosa Torres OBITUARY

Raquel Rosa Torres 8/20/1917- 8/16/2012 Resident of Mountain View Beloved wife of the late Roberto M. Torres; loving mother of the late John E. Torres, Rosa passed away peacefully at home of natural causes with family by her side on August 16, 2012. A devoted mother who deeply cared for her family, animals and strangers alike, she leaves behind 14 children, 23 grandkids, 26 great-grandkids, and 3 great-great grandkids. Mom, we bid you an eternal farewell to our Heavenly Father.

Neptune Society 916-574-7870
